rce\": \"transcript\",\n      \"source_type\": \"raw_archive\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-04-30 09:02\",\n      \"id\": 8755,\n      \"preview\": \"## Memory summary\\n\\nThis 10-minute window captured four parallel threads: AtlasCloud Turbowan 2.2 SVI rollout validation in `aip`, remote `harness` workflow/state-machine review over RustDesk, `looper` social-draft and Grok-output cleanup work, and `rss-scout` URL-normalization changes. The highest-s\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"session_id\": \"019ddd9d-8b61-77d3-b56a-668aa5250a8a\",\n      \"source\": \"hook\",\n      \"source_type\": \"raw_archive\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"branch\": \"main\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-04-29 00:25\",\n      \"id\": 3796,\n      \"preview\": \"Base directory for this skill: /Users/lifcc/.claude/skills/x-post\\n\\n# X 原创资产构建器\\n\\n**定位：把 reply 带来的注意力，转成主页认知、主题资产和可复用内容。**\\n\\n**禁止编造。禁止营销腔。禁止暴露自动化运营。没有亲身经验或本地证据就跳过。**\\n\\ncurrent_version: v11.6\\n\\n> 主文件只放当前执行合约。历史版本见 `references/changelog.md`；图片 prompt 细节见 `references/image-policy.md`；长范例按需打开 references，不要一次\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/life/x\",\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"session_id\": \"46848609-d3c3-4f5d-beb0-2358209e1a84\",\n      \"source\": \"transcript\",\n      \"source_type\": \"raw_archive\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-04-28 15:09\",\n      \"id\": 3509,\n      \"preview\": \"## Memory summary\\n\\nDuring this 10-minute window, the user continued two parallel workstreams.\\n\\nFirst, in `~/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om`, they were validating the local CRE Studio / OM generation flow for the Trylon Tower fixture tied to deal ID `2ce0ac8c-255c-40d3-930a-8c4d380ca79a`. Browser state s\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"