{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_23","type":"mcp_tool_call","server":"remem","tool":"search","arguments":{"query":"└─ Budget SessionStart footer","limit":20,"include_stale":true},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"has_more\": true,\n  \"mode\": \"compact\",\n  \"next_offset\": 20,\n  \"next_step\": {\n    \"ids\": [\n      76063,\n      20512,\n      20583,\n      76849,\n      65115,\n      75979,\n      75953,\n      75936,\n      79244,\n      64851,\n      66704,\n      67126,\n      76036,\n      65654,\n      15351,\n      65675,\n      15326,\n      14327,\n      15337,\n      20548\n    ],\n    \"reason\": \"Pass selected compact result IDs with source='memory' to fetch full details.\",\n    \"source\": \"memory\",\n    \"tool\": \"get_observations\"\n  },\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"has_more\": true,\n    \"limit\": 20,\n    \"next_offset\": 20,\n    \"offset\": 0\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 76063,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 为 remem memory library hardening 完成 v0.4.1 发布，并把 crates.io `remem-ai` 自动发布接入 GitHub Actions release workflow，]\\n\\nSessionStart truncation 必须保留 context stats footer。v0.4.1 取代 v0.4.0 作为最新发布版本\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/remem\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"SessionStart truncation 必须保留 context stats footer。v0.4.1 取代 v0.4.0 作为最新发布版本 — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-55a6cd5a9c29aeeb\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-16 08:12\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 20512,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 修复 om-generator-web ProformaLayout 数据表格超过可用区高度、无法单页铺满的问题（表格需 988px 但可用区仅 859px）]\\n\\n页脚 121px（divider + footer）是设计意图，不可侵占\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om/om-generator-web\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"页脚 121px（divider + footer）是设计意图，不可侵占 — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-1c2eea5f6e237dbf\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-08 08:16\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 20583,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 修复 om-generator-web ProformaLayout 数据表格超过可用区高度（表格 988px vs 可用区 859px 溢出 129px）— 实现单页铺满渲染]\\n\\n页脚 121px 不可侵占（设计常数，divider + footer）（高）\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om/om-generator-web\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"页脚 121px 不可侵占（设计常数，divider + footer）（高） — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-922614bbfab34ee1\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-08 08:45\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 76849,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 推进 PageLingo/chenjinshi Chrome MV3 扩展接近 Immersive Translate parity，]\\n\\nRTF 解析选择翻译普通 `\\\\header` / `\\\\footer` 可见文本，因为页眉页脚是用户可见内容；继续拒绝翻译图片、对象、字段指令、样式表等控制目的地。\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"RTF 解析选择翻译普通 `\\\\header` / `\\\\footer` 可见文本， — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-867e853008dd24a3\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-19 00:16\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 65115,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: Diagnose and fix X reply throughput bottleneck in Looper system while preserving quality anchors (v14 contract gate, 1/day single-author cap);]\\n\\nTreat knowledge-scout report as heterogeneous (heterogeneous sections + footer blocks) rather than homogeneous batch source\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Treat knowledge-scout report as heterogeneous (heterogeneous sections + footer blocks) rather than — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-f2ed15453255f098\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-05 08:13\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 75979,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: Review PR #166 for remem CLI search parity, especially `--multi-hop` behavior with new search filters `--branch`, `--offset`, `--include-stale`,]\\n\\notherwise CLI search parity is broken. Pending dry-run and context footer preservation were reviewed and not considered blocking.\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/remem\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"otherwise CLI search parity is broken. Pending dry-run and context footer preservation were reviewed and — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-dac07270d63e4af3\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-16 04:15\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 75953,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 用户要求为 remem memory library hardening 工作写完整 spec、开 GitHub issues、实现并提交 PR，]\\n\\nCLI search 改用 canonical memory-service search，避免 CLI 与 memory-service 搜索语义分叉。pending-observation mutation 增加 dry-run mode，以便安全检查 failed pending observations，不直接修改真实数据。SessionStart output truncation 必须保留 context sta\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/remem\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"CLI search 改用 canonical memory-service search，避免 CLI 与 memory-service 搜索语义分叉。 — decisions\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-81f848af8c631dac\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-16 03:45\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 75936,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 用户要求为 remem memory library hardening 工作写完整 spec、开 GitHub issues、实现并提交 PR，]\\n\\nCLI search 应改用 canonical memory-service search，避免 CLI 与 memory-service 搜索语义分叉。pending-observation mutation 增加 dry-run mode，以便安全检查 failed pending observations，不直接修改真实数据。SessionStart output truncation 必须保留 context st\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/remem\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"CLI search 应改用 canonical memory-service search，避免 CLI 与 memory-service 搜索语义分叉。 — decisions\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-ffef2f24d9065176\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-16 03:31\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 79244,\n      \"preview\": \"Prepared local bugfix for PageLingo visual-site audit findings (not yet submitted as GitHub issue/PR; external action still needs user confirmation). Symptom: Wistia blog translated nav/footer/subscription chrome, Coursera fixture lecture URLs translated auth-shell text like 'Log in or create accoun\",\n      \"project\": \"chenjinshi\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Prepared PageLingo Wistia/Coursera/Zoom site chrome exclusions\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"wistia-coursera-zoom-site-chrome-exclusions\",\n      \"type\": \"bugfix\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-31 08:54\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 64851,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 诊断 multi-post batch 流水线中 split_sections.sh 和 run_batch.sh 的问题：section footer 混入、Reddit-no-fetch sections 被送到 codex]\\n\\n**split_sections.sh 边界修复（Patch 1）**：改为在 `^### \\\\d+\\\\.` 或 `^## ` 任一处停止，避免收入 scout footer\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/life/looper\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"**split_sections.sh 边界修复（Patch 1）**：改为在 `^### \\\\d+\\\\. — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-3c36c502ad65e22e\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-05 01:48\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 66704,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 规划 knowledge-scout digest → X post draft 的筛选与自动生成流程，维护 `x-post`/`multi-post` SKILL 版本更新与 commit 策略。]\\n\\nsection footer 新判定：`## ` 后不跟数字（例 `## Bridge 1` 为 footer 而非 section）\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/life/looper\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"section footer 新判定：`## ` 后不跟数字（例 `## Bridge 1` 为 footer 而非 section） — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-86e91bd0bc5effd2\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-06 09:47\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 67126,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 规划并执行 knowledge-scout digest → X post draft 自动生成流程，维护 `x-post`/`multi-post` SKILL 版本更新、imagegen/ChatGPT]\\n\\nsection footer 新判定：`## ` 后不跟数字（例 `## Bridge 1`）为 footer 而非 section。\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/life/looper\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"section footer 新判定：`## ` 后不跟数字（例 `## Bridge 1`）为 footer 而非 section。 — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-e77f31ba90fb666e\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-06 14:27\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 76036,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 为 remem memory library hardening 工作完成整个发布周期：写 spec、开 GitHub issues、实现 multi-hop search filter propagation]\\n\\nCLI search 改用 canonical memory-service 搜索避免语义分叉。multi-hop search filters（`--branch`、`--memory-type`、`--include-stale`、`--offset`）必须端到端传递到第一/二跳 entity/FTS expansion 和最终 pagination，off\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/remem\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"CLI search 改用 canonical memory-service 搜索避免语义分叉。 — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-064b3b23347af4c1\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-16 06:12\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 65654,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: User wanted a persistent memory summary of a Claude Code screen-recording session validating the Knowledge Scout → Looper/X `multi-post` pipeline,]\\n\\nFooter/boundary parsing must stop around the report bridge/footer area to avoid non-section material entering draft generation.\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Footer/boundary parsing must stop around the report bridge/footer area to avoid non-section material — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-ed6554b397b0ace4\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-05 16:23\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 15351,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: om-generator-web 中去除表格编辑器重复代码、拆分超限文件、编写3层分层单元测试，]\\n\\nconvertRowKind是行类型转换关键函数，支持data↔category/data→title/footer路由\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om/om-generator-web/workspace\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"convertRowKind是行类型转换关键函数，支持data↔category/data→title/footer路由 — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-d21b22e8600eeae3\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-02 22:10\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 65675,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 规划并执行 knowledge-scout digest（知识侦察摘要）到 X post draft 的筛选与生成流程，]\\n\\nsection footer 的新判定：`## ` 后不跟数字（例如`## Bridge 1`）；section 22 仍是最后有效 section。\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/life/looper\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"section footer 的新判定：`## ` 后不跟数字（例如`## Bridge 1`）； — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-098cc7842b80ee00\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-06 09:38\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 15326,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 完成 om-generator-web 表格编辑器工具函数的单元测试，遵循 3 层测试分层规范（正常路径、边界情况、错误路径），]\\n\\nconvertRowKind 是行类型转换关键函数，支持 data↔category/data→title/footer，影响 schema 解析\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om/om-generator-web/workspace\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"convertRowKind 是行类型转换关键函数，支持 data↔category/data→title/footer， — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-3517cd6c88938bab\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-02 21:48\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 14327,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 修复 om-generator-web CardEditor 表格和正文段落无法编辑，探索 Plate.js 原生表格集成方案]\\n\\nOM 财务表格的 11 种 RowKind（header/data/subtotal/noi/footer 等）决定行样式，Plate 原生表格没有此概念\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om/om-generator-web\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"OM 财务表格的 11 种 RowKind（header/data/subtotal/noi/footer 等）决定行样式， — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-7bba84e65d151aeb\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-02 09:31\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 15337,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 完成 om-generator-web 全量文件拆分重构（U-16: 200-400 行典型、800 行上限）、编写 30+ 单元测试（3]\\n\\nconvertRowKind 是行类型转换关键函数，支持 data↔category/data→title/footer，分支覆盖率要求 100%\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om/om-generator-web/workspace\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"convertRowKind 是行类型转换关键函数，支持 data↔category/data→title/footer， — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-6b8f1f0fe114839c\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-02 21:57\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 20548,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 修复 om-generator-web ProformaLayout 数据表格超过可用区高度（表格 988px vs 可用 859px 溢出 129px）]\\n\\n真实可用 content 高度公式验证：1080 - 100(content.top) - 121(footer) = 859px 精确\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om/om-generator-web\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"真实可用 content 高度公式验证：1080 - 100(content.top) - 121(footer) = 859px 精确 — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-65dbc43464225640\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-08 08:37\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"structured_content":null},"error":null,"status":"completed"}}
